{"lemma":"بَرَى","slug":"بَرَى","root":"ب.ر.#","root_slug":"ب-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2422"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wild"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"overland, land, terrestrial"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"بَرّ (barr, “land”) + ـِيّ (-iyy)."},"ipa":["/bar.riː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2422","headword_ar":"بَرَى","root":"brY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, K,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barayotu","text_ar":"بَرَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroYN","text_ar":"بَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He formed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashioned, by cutting; shaped out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pared;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T, M, K;) a reed for writing, (Lth, As, ISk, T, S, M, Msb,) and a stick, or piece of wood, (Lth, T, M,) and an arrow, (M, K,) &c.; (M;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtrY","text_ar":"ابترى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barawotu","text_ar":"بَرَوْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, T,) is a dial. var., (Msb,) used by some, who say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huma yaqoluw Albur~a","text_ar":"هُمَ يَقْلُو البُرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqoliY","text_ar":"يَقْلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, T.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (As, T,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (As, T, M, K,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded, and made to lose flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, * T, * S,) a she-camel, (As, T,) or a camel: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(journeying)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered"},{"kind":"text","text":"him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) and in like manner one says of a year of dearth or drought. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barayotu sanaAmahaA bisayoriY EalayohaA","text_ar":"بَرَيْتُ سَنَامَهَا بِسَيْرِى عَلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I wasted her hump by my journeying upon her"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: occurring in a poem of El-Aashà. (M.)       -A2-  See also 3: ―         -b2-  and see 5, in two places."}],"source_refs":["T","M","K","S","Msb","Lth","As","ISk"]}]}}